{"3711590": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "45號電車", "steam_appid": 3711590, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3711590/extras/c9bac5b7493de380051733df3045d87e.avif?t=1768888574\" width=1560 height=878 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆遊戲介紹</h2>你像往常一樣搭著電車，忽然就被捲入了一個異世界！<br>當你睜開眼，發現自己與兩位陌生少女困在一班永無終點的神秘列車上。<br>這裡沒有司機、沒有乘客，只有無盡的車廂與逐漸扭曲的現實。<br>來自不同背景的你們，被一位自稱「柯尼亞爾」的列車主人指派調查列車內的異常現象。<br>隨著探索的深入，情感與慾望交織，而這班列車的真正目的，也將漸漸浮現......<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆角色簡介</h2><br><strong>高橋怜奈 Reina Takahashi</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3711590/extras/ece44af2f44f270dfbc6257140bea4cb.poster.avif?t=1768888574\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3711590/extras/ece44af2f44f270dfbc6257140bea4cb.webm?t=1768888574\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3711590/extras/ece44af2f44f270dfbc6257140bea4cb.mp4?t=1768888574\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>與男主年齡相仿的女性上班族，理性而內斂，總是默默支撐著大家的情緒。<br><br><strong>朝倉 舞 Mai Asakura</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3711590/extras/c8b186f119c2e637c351c44a2cc7f01d.poster.avif?t=1768888574\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3711590/extras/c8b186f119c2e637c351c44a2cc7f01d.webm?t=1768888574\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3711590/extras/c8b186f119c2e637c351c44a2cc7f01d.mp4?t=1768888574\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>陽光開朗的金髮辣妹，擅長用笑容化解緊張氣氛。看似隨性，卻在關鍵時刻展現堅定一面。<br><br><strong>柯尼亞爾 Konial</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3711590/extras/865e6c77616c497fc6783b79b372fe23.poster.avif?t=1768888574\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3711590/extras/865e6c77616c497fc6783b79b372fe23.webm?t=1768888574\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3711590/extras/865e6c77616c497fc6783b79b372fe23.mp4?t=1768888574\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>自稱為這班異世界列車的主人，帶著戲謔與掌控欲。她藏著無人知曉的目的，也似乎對你有異樣的好感！？<br><br><strong>帕祖祖 Pazuzu</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3711590/extras/bc79497fa51e321d6c51566d94a47970.poster.avif?t=1768888574\" width=780 height=438 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3711590/extras/bc79497fa51e321d6c51566d94a47970.webm?t=1768888574\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3711590/extras/bc79497fa51e321d6c51566d94a47970.mp4?t=1768888574\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>怯懦卻堅持正義的天使，自願潛入列車調查柯尼亞爾的罪行。外表看似溫柔可親，內心卻蘊藏著截然不同的真實面貌。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3711590/extras/2343d23570ec4a68ebb04f57ccb74a89.poster.avif?t=1768888574\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3711590/extras/2343d23570ec4a68ebb04f57ccb74a89.webm?t=1768888574\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3711590/extras/2343d23570ec4a68ebb04f57ccb74a89.mp4?t=1768888574\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆遊戲玩法</h2><strong>異象偵查 × 車廂探索</strong><br>在每一個章節中，玩家需穿梭於列車車廂之間，找出場景中浮現的異象。這些異象牽動故事進展，也會影響同行角色的情緒與關係。<br><br><strong>情感系統 × 多重結局</strong><br>隨著劇情選擇與探索互動，旅伴對你的情感將逐步加深，進而解鎖專屬事件與不同結局路線。角色之間的情感，正是通往結局的關鍵！<br><br><strong>裝備系統 × 高效探索</strong><br>透過在車廂中獲得道具與提升好感度，可兌換特殊裝備，提升觀察力與解謎效率。遊戲中後段可解鎖特殊的模式，進入隱藏路線。<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3711590/extras/d9fa824ef3e38c4748ef9170f6f5c131.avif?t=1768888574\" width=1560 height=880 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆遊戲特色</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>4位可攻略女角<br></li><li>40張以上的HCG<br></li><li>全日文配音</li></ul><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3711590/extras/33917e72a73e4f22f9da61a1fe61f334.poster.avif?t=1768888574\" width=1170 height=658 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3711590/extras/33917e72a73e4f22f9da61a1fe61f334.webm?t=1768888574\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3711590/extras/33917e72a73e4f22f9da61a1fe61f334.mp4?t=1768888574\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>", "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3711590/extras/c9bac5b7493de380051733df3045d87e.avif?t=1768888574\" width=1560 height=878 /></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆遊戲介紹</h2>你像往常一樣搭著電車，忽然就被捲入了一個異世界！<br>當你睜開眼，發現自己與兩位陌生少女困在一班永無終點的神秘列車上。<br>這裡沒有司機、沒有乘客，只有無盡的車廂與逐漸扭曲的現實。<br>來自不同背景的你們，被一位自稱「柯尼亞爾」的列車主人指派調查列車內的異常現象。<br>隨著探索的深入，情感與慾望交織，而這班列車的真正目的，也將漸漸浮現......<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >◆角色簡介</h2><br><strong>高橋怜奈 Reina Takahashi</strong><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akama